<br>
There are significant advantages to having 2 hate proc weapons, and I do count on that proc every fight.  In long fights like Burrower Parasite, High priest, Cursed, or whatever, I ussually die or get charmed.  After getting rezzed or  uncharmed I don't have the luxuary of solo time on a mob, 2 hate weapons allows me to come back and get right on top of the agro list ussually within 30 seconds from begining dead bottom.<br>
<br>
Climbing the hate list would take much longer with my older weapons, they are now inadiquate for effectively tuanting off our crazy ass wizards. <br>
