<br>
Call me odd but I use a LOT of weapons, including the sapper.   I've found that in my weapons kit, I can reliably hold aggro BEST using the following combination.<br>
<br>
Veldrak's Shortblade<br>
Veridix's Shortsword<br>
<br>
DPS is the suck (at 13/23 and 14/23) but the proc is INSANE aggro (Force Shock, which is 179DD+Stun).  This weapons combo has proven to be the most reliable set in my arsenal, and they're easy as pie to get if your guild is VP/manaburn enabled.<br>
<br>
IMO this is the single best pre-Hategiver/BoC/BF weapon in game for those who arent' lucky enough to enter ST while the warders are still up.   <br>
<br>
Having said that, the &quot;dps&quot; argument is also relatively irrelevant against high mitigation Luclin mobs because there's no effective difference between a 13/20 weapon and a 3/20 weapon when all you're hitting for is 1's and 12's.  How do I know this?  The last time I tanked in Ssra, I brought with me a couple of gnoll hide lariats.....guess what....I OWNED on aggro and did the same parsed damage as with sapper/primal.<br>
<br>
Finally...for aggro control.....solve this and become a true master...<br>
<br>
Aggro godliness takes many forms, the one which appears to be crap is the closest to the divine. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ualien1099.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alien1099</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 414<br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/26/02 7:04:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1700.topic&index=31>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.home.com/alien1099/alien.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Aggro</span><hr size=1> The original poster said he was losing agro with this Willsapper so I would assume he wanted a better agro weapon, not DPS. In reference to Gore's post, I'd reread the original post before thinking some posters' logic is flawed next time. <p><p><font face="verdana, arial" size="-2"><u><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6885" target=top>Gerald Swiftblades</a></u> [<a href="http://www.darkblood.com" target=top><i>Darkblood</i></a>]<br>
